final_desc: - Umbi, bonggol, akar berbonggol, batang dibawah tanah, tajuk dan akar tongkat, sedang tumbuh atau berbunga; tanaman dan akar chicory :Umbi, bonggol, akar berbonggol, batang dibawah tanah, tajuk dan akar tongkat, dorman, sedang tumbuh atau berbunga; tanaman dan akar chicory selain akar dari pos 12.12.;- Bulbs, tubers, tuberous roots, corms, crowns and rhizomes, in growth or in flower; chicory plants and roots :Bulbs, tubers, tuberous roots, corms, crowns and rhizomes, dormant, in growth or in flower; chicory plants and roots other than roots of heading 12.12.
